#

Herb-Infused Pork Chops with Red Wine Gravy and Truffle Mashed Potatoes

$25.99
750 kcal
Difficulty: 60%

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

Comfort FoodGourmetMain Course

Description

Juicy pork chops infused with fresh herbs, topped with a rich red wine gravy, served alongside creamy truffle mashed potatoes for an indulgent meal.

Ingredients

  • Pork Chops: 4 (bone-in)
  • Fresh Thyme: 2 tablespoons
  • Fresh Rosemary: 2 tablespoons
  • Garlic: 4 cloves, minced
  • Olive Oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black Pepper: to taste
  • Red Wine: 1 cup
  • Beef Broth: 1 cup
  • Butter: 3 tablespoons
  • Mashed Potatoes: 2 pounds, peeled and cubed
  • Truffle Oil: 1 tablespoon
  • Heavy Cream: 1/2 cup
  • Chives: for garnish
